23 Feb 2017 21:56






I've never written an SCP before, and frankly I'm a bit nervous to put this up for judgment, but I'm pretty sure there's no point where I wouldn't be.

Many thanks to the people on the forum and on Reddit who gave me some critique!

Edit2:  I rewrote the test logs. I took some of your criticisms into account, and I realized I had two main goals - to describe some interesting planets and to explain the specific properties of the wormhole. This led to two major changes. First, all the old planet descriptions were scrapped. Second, there are now two experiment logs - a  describing the actual planets the Foundation explores through the anomaly. I also added an event at the end, to try and showcase some of the dangers this object might hold despite existing containment procedures.





